				<div class="flex items-start mb-6">
					<div class="bg-green-100 rounded-xl p-4 mr-6">
						<svg class="h-10 w-10 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
							<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6 2a1 1 0 00-1 1v1H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2h-1V3a1 1 0 10-2 0v1H7V3a1 1 0 00-1-1zm0 5a1 1 0 000 2h8a1 1 0 100-2H6z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<div class="flex-1">
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 heading-font mb-3">Roofing Process Timeline</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 font-medium mb-4 leading-relaxed">
							Day-by-day breakdown of what happens during your roofing project.
							Know exactly what to expect from start to finish.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="mb-6">
					<h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 heading-font text-sm">What You'll Learn:</h4>
					<ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 font-medium">
						<li class="flex items-center">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-600 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
							Pre-installation preparation steps
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-600 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
							Tear-off and inspection process
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-600 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
							Installation quality checkpoints
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-600 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
							Final cleanup and walkthrough
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
					<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-bold rounded-full heading-font">Timeline</span>
					<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs font-bold rounded-full heading-font">Process</span>
					<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 text-xs font-bold rounded-full heading-font">Quality</span>
				</div>

