						<h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 heading-font mb-3">Maintenance & Care Guide</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 font-medium mb-4 leading-relaxed">
							Seasonal maintenance calendar and care instructions to protect your investment
