						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="mb-6">
					<h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 heading-font text-sm">What You'll Learn:</h4>
					<ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 font-medium">
						<li class="flex items-center">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
							Spring, summer, fall, winter tasks
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
							Warning signs to watch for
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
							DIY vs professional guidance
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
							Maintenance record keeping
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
					<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs font-bold rounded-full heading-font">Seasonal</span>
					<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-bold rounded-full heading-font">Preventive</span>
					<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-orange-100 text-orange-800 text-xs font-bold rounded-full heading-font">Care Tips</span>
				</div>

				<a href="/maintenance-guide" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors font-bold heading-font">
					View Maintenance Guide
					<svg class="ml-2 h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
					</svg>
				</a>
			</div>

