							Emergency protocols and immediate response steps for Kansas City's severe weather.
							Be prepared before the storm hits.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="mb-6">
					<h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 heading-font text-sm">What You'll Learn:</h4>
					<ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 font-medium">
						<li class="flex items-center">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-600 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
							24-hour emergency response checklist
